OL,6,CG1973FThe Eurovision Song Contest airs
OL,7,Fon BBC One. Live from Luxembourg. It
OL,8,Fwas won by Anne-Marie David with Tu te
OL,9,Freconnaitras. The United Kingdom was
OL,10,Frepresented by Cliff Richard - singing
OL,11,FPower to All Our Friends - and finished
OL,12,Fthird. The show was watched by 21.56m.
